nodes.text: The Bubble Wink was a Outer Rim Territories hyperspace route that connected the worlds of Rampa in the Corporate Sector and Panna in the Cronese Mandate. The former pirate Queen Maz Kanata listed it as one of the "real" trade routes to be used by smugglers, as opposed to the official ones, in the book that would become known as the Smuggler's Guide.
The Bubble Wink was first mentioned in Star Wars: Smuggler's Guide, a reference book written by Daniel Wallace and released in 2018.
